Package: bayesDiagnostics
Type: Package
Title: Comprehensive Bayesian Model Diagnostics and Comparison
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Ikramul", "Rakib", , "ikrakib1010@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides comprehensive tools for Bayesian model diagnostics 
    and comparison. Includes prior sensitivity analysis, posterior predictive 
    checks, advanced model comparison, convergence diagnostics, and prior 
    elicitation tools. Integrates with rstan, brms, and rstanarm.
